cvmx_rad_mem_debug1

This CSR is a memory of 256 entries, and thus, the RAD_REG_READ_IDX CSR must be written before any CSR read operations to this address can be performed. A read of any entry that has not been previously written is illegal and will result in unpredictable CSR read data.
